## Overall App Grade: **A−**

The architecture quality is now genuinely excellent. The 9-section nav with shell delegation, `ARCHITECTURE_OBJECTIVES` as policy-as-code, `FORWARD_PLATFORM_CONTROLS` covering every emerging Snowflake platform risk, the mart SQL factory, deterministic Ask OVERWATCH, and the lazy export system together form a coherent, production-grade platform. The only things keeping this from a full **A** are the personal email in the public repo (fix immediately), the unconfirmed `build_platform_futures_board` function (could be a deploy blocker), and the App Performance pane that has been misleading in SiS for four consecutive reviews. Fix items 1 and 2 today. Everything else is polish.